data.description: Discover modern, urban living at it's finest in this stunning end unit. Located just minutes from 66 and walkable to local shopping centers, this contemporary residence offers the perfect blend of style, convenience,  and comfort. Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the sleek and open living space, illuminated by box window. The living room flows seamlessly into the dinning and kitchen,creating an ideal setting for entertaining and everyday living. The kitchen is a masterpiece, featuring top of the line appliances and brand new quartz countertops. Whether you're a gourmet chef or simply enjoy cooking, this kitchen will delight your culinary senses. The unit boasts a spacious primary suite with a beautiful shower stall including glass barn doors and rain shower head, creating a tranquil oasis for relaxation.  Primary also includes ample closet space and built in vanity.  All bathrooms have been updated. Step outside to your freshly sealed private deck, where you can savor your morning coffee while soaking in the sun or your evening cocktail with friends. Recreational room in basement has a lovely brick fireplace and waterproof LVP flooring. Laundry room also located in basement.  New windows installed throughout home in 2020.  Exterior was newly painted in 2022. Access to Community pool and walking trails. Perfectly situated near shops, restaurants, and grocery stores, you'll relish the vibrant lifestyle this location offers. Whether you are looking for a chic residence or a place to call home, this unit is a must see opportunity. Come make this beautiful home yours!!!
